node.text:
This is your last chance to enter to win the GLOCK Gearbox as we wrap-up #NationalShootingSportsMonth. Click the link in our bio to enter. 

Thank you to all who've participated this month and to NSSF for advocating the importance of the shooting sports industry.

#LetsGoShooting #GLOCKperfection #NationalShootingSportsMonth #NationalShootingSportsFoundation #GLOCK #shootGLOCK #PlusOneMovement #NSSM #NSSF

Team GLOCK was able to bring home a few wins over the weekend at the USPSA Area 8 Championship in Hedgesville, WV at Shadow Hawk Defense. 

@shane_coley won High Overall in Limited Division shooting his G24 and @scuzi23 won High Lady in Production shooting her G34.

"With September being the last competition month before Nationals, this was a great start to the final training cycle." 
-Shane Coley, Team GLOCK Captain

Way to go Team GLOCK! 💥 

#GLOCKon #GLOCKcompete #competitiveshooting #ThisIsTeamGLOCK

node.text:
Keeping our United States Military in our thoughts & prayers.

REPOST FROM @marines:

"UPDATE: We can confirm, at this time, that 11 Marines were killed in the line of duty at Hamid Karzai International Airport. This is an update to the information we provided yesterday.

We continue to mourn the loss of these Marines, and pray for their families. Our focus now is taking care of the families of those who were killed, and caring for the injured. The identities of those killed will be withheld until 24 hours after all next-of-kin notifications are complete."

node.text:
"A few years ago, I learned this little trick (see my dominant hand on the gun) from a couple of my IG friends. It involves wrapping the thumb up and over the rear of the slide upon establishing grip from holster.

Prior to implementing this technique, I struggled to get a consistent purchase when drawing from concealment, which was one of my biggest frustrations. Now, I get a consistent high, tight grip every time and it’s made a big impact on my training.

What’s one small adjustment that made a huge difference in your training?"
- @pinotandpistols

📸: @kenzers
👤: @pinotandpistols

#repost #glockperfection #GLOCK #concealcarry #glockcarry #womenwhocarry #g48 #glockslimline #everydaycarry #GLOCKon

node.text:
The heart of competition season is here!

Over the weekend, Shane Coley & Ashley Rheuark with Team GLOCK competed at the USPSA Area 1 Championship in Puyallup, WA. 
@ashley_rheuark won High Lady in Carry Optics Division with her G34MOS and @shane_coley won High Overall in Limited Division with his G24. 

Keep up the hard work, Team GLOCK 👊 

#competitiveshooting #rangetime
